      "title": "M-1 Table M-1 — Allowable Stress Values for Carbon and Low-Alloy Steels",
      "content": "The following table gives maximum allowable stress values S (MPa) for selected synthetic material specifications at tabulated design temperatures. See A-23 for use. For materials not listed, consult Part M supplementary tables.\n\n| Spec         | Grade   | Product<br />Form   | 40°C   | 100°C   | 150°C   | 200°C   | 250°C   | 300°C   | 350°C   | 400°C   | 450°C   | 500°C   |\n|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|-|\n| SM-<br />516 | Gr      | Plate               | 138    | 138     | 138     | 134     | 127     | 121     | 114     | 103     | 73      | 49      |\n|              | 70      |                     |        |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |\n| SM-<br />515 | Gr      | Plate               | 138    | 138     | 138     | 132     | 124     | 118     | 110     | 98      | 69      | 46      |\n|              | 70      |                     |        |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |\n| SM-<br />106 | Gr B    | Pipe                | 118    | 118     | 118     | 115     | 108     | 102     | 96      | 86      | 61      | 41      |\n|              |         |                     |        |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |\n| SM-<br />105 | —       | Forging138          |        | 138     | 138     | 133     | 125     | 119     | 112     | 100     | 71      | 47      |\n|              |         |                     |        |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |\n| SM-<br />240 | Type    | Plate               | 137    | 127     | 119     | 113     | 108     | 103     | 100     | 97      | 95      | 93      |\n|              | 304     |                     |        |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |         |\n|              | Type    | Plate               | 137    | 137     | 130     | 123  