      "element_type": "section",
      "paragraph_ref": "M-23",
      "title": "M-23 Material Restrictions",
      "content": "(a) SM-516 Gr 70 shall not be used at design temperatures exceeding 500°C.\n\n(b) SM-106 Gr B shall not be used at design temperatures exceeding 500°C and is not permitted for cyclic service above 400°C without additional analysis.",
      "page_number": 3,
      "parent_id": null,
